Paper: hep-th/9803147

Date: 1998-03-18

Title: Some Observations on Broken Symmetries

Authors: M. Testa

Comments: 13 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: JHEP 9804 (1998) 002

We present a general analysis of the field theoretical properties whichguarantee the recovery, at the renormalized level, of symmetries broken byregularization. We also discuss the anomalous case.